you just send back to a store?

252
00:39:43.640 --> 00:39:46.074
I love you. I'm not going anywhere.

253
00:39:47.320 --> 00:39:50.995
You give Joseph 20.000
for month number one.

254
00:39:51.120 --> 00:39:53.076
What are you doing?

255
00:39:54.880 --> 00:39:59.271
- You give him 25.000 for month two.
- Doesn't anything mean anything?

256
00:40:01.280 --> 00:40:04.716
- I'm your woman. you're my man.
- 30.000 for the third.

257
00:40:13.240 --> 00:40:16.550
Frank. Frank. I made a commitment.

258
00:40:16.680 --> 00:40:19.035
To hell with me.

259
00:40:19.160 --> 00:40:21.993
with you. with everything.

260
00:40:25.720 --> 00:40:28.075
I'm throwing you out.

261
00:40:34.840 --> 00:40:36.592
Get out.

262
00:40:44.400 --> 00:40:45.992
Get out.

263
00:40:54.520 --> 00:40:56.476
Get out!

264
00:41:06.040 --> 00:41:07.996
<i>(baby cries)</i>

265
00:41:50.600 --> 00:41:52.556
<i>(rustling leaves)</i>

266
00:46:25.000 --> 00:46:27.116
You want some milk?

267
00:46:27.240 --> 00:46:29.196
No. I'm OK.

268
00:49:57.200 --> 00:49:58.952
Argh!

269
00:55:32.880 --> 00:55:36.429
Visiontext Subtitles: Adrian Isaac

270
00:56:01.880 --> 00:56:03.836
ENHOH

